### シフト最適化（非同期）- ジョブ投入
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/solve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employees": [
    {
      "id": "emp1",
      "name": "田中太郎",
      "skills": ["看護師", "フルタイム"]
    }
  ],
  "shifts": [
    {
      "id": "shift1",
      "start_time": "2025-06-01T09:00:00",
      "end_time": "2025-06-01T17:00:00",
      "required_skills": ["看護師"]
    }
  ]
}

### ジョブ結果取得（上記レスポンスのjob_idを使用）
# GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/solve/{job_id}

